{
  "texts": [
    "Federated Instruction Tuning on Financial DatasetExperimental setups.",
    "We use a financial sentiment analysis dataset 3 as the training dataset [83,67].",
    "During training, we set the client number as 50, where we randomly sample 5 clients to be available for each round.",
    "These clients hold 10k data samples in total.",
    "During the evaluation, we consider four financial sentiment analysis benchmarks, including FPB [80], FIQA-SA [81], TFNS [82], and NWGI [83], where both accuracy and F1 score are measured."
  ]
}